Count Occurrences of Characters
Write a Java program to count the frequency of each character in a given string.
Sample Input
banana
Sample Output
b : 1
a : 3
n : 2


Coding..:
import java.util.*;
class occurance{
    public void frequency(char c[]){
        for(int i=0;i<=c.length;i++){
        int count=0,a=0;
        for(int j=0;j<i;j++){
            if(c[i]==c[j]){
                count++;
                break;
            }
        }
        if(count==1){
            continue;
        }
        for(int j=0;j<c.length;j++){
            if(c[i]==c[j]){
                a++;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(c[i]+":"+a);
        a=0;
    }
}
    }
    
public class Main{
    public static void main(String args[]){
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        String a=sc.nextLine();
        char[] arr=a.toCharArray();
        occurance Freq=new occurance();
        Freq.frequency(arr);
    }
}
